      • reason

        @Nullable
public abstract java.lang.String reason()
        Notification reason. It is valid only if type() is DirectionsCriteria.NOTIFICATION_TYPE_ALERT and subtype() is DirectionsCriteria.NOTIFICATION_SUBTYPE_EV_STATION_UNAVAILABLE.
        Returns:
        reason for the unavailability of the charging station for the electric vehicle

      • chargingStationId

        @Nullable
 @SerializedName(value="station_id")
public abstract java.lang.String chargingStationId()
        Notification charging station id. It is valid only if type() is DirectionsCriteria.NOTIFICATION_TYPE_ALERT and subtype() is DirectionsCriteria.NOTIFICATION_SUBTYPE_EV_STATION_UNAVAILABLE.
        Returns:
        charging station id of the unavailable charging station for the electric vehicle
